e":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2757754886/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2757754886","tinyui":"/x/BgBgp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2757754886","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2757754886/Documentaci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2757754886"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<h1>Feature Branch</h1><p>feature/pix-service</p><h1>Proyectos involucrados</h1><ul><li><p>bancard-pix-service</p></li><li><p>&hellip;</p></li></ul><h1>Consideraciones Generales</h1><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"a9eb4f91-51a2-421a-a5ce-451a3ef1b84b\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 554.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 204.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p /></th><th><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><ac:emoticon ac:name=\"blue-star\" ac:emoji-shortname=\":white_check_mark:\" ac:emoji-id=\"2705\" ac:emoji-fallback=\"✅\" />  o  <ac:emoticon ac:name=\"cross\" ac:emoji-shortname=\":cross_mark:\" ac:emoji-id=\"atlassian-cross_mark\" ac:emoji-fallback=\":cross_mark:\" /> </p></th></tr><tr><td><p>Necesita cambios en la configuraci&oacute;n</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><ac:emoticon ac:name=\"blue-star\" ac:emoji-shortname=\":white_check_mark:\" ac:emoji-id=\"2705\" ac:emoji-fallback=\"✅\" /></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Necesita conexi&oacute;n con servicios externos (Coordinar con Denis).</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><ac:emoticon ac:name=\"blue-star\" ac:emoji-shortname=\":white_check_mark:\" ac:emoji-id=\"2705\" ac:emoji-fallback=\"✅\" /></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Necesita conexi&oacute;n con otros servidores (Revisar conectividad y coordinar con Denis).</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><ac:emoticon ac:name=\"blue-star\" ac:emoji-shortname=\":white_check_mark:\" ac:emoji-id=\"2705\" ac:emoji-fallback=\"✅\" /></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Necesita ejecutar migraciones en la db (Coordinar con DBA).</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><ac:emoticon ac:name=\"blue-star\" ac:emoji-shortname=\":white_check_mark:\" ac:emoji-id=\"2705\" ac:emoji-fallback=\"✅\" /></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Necesita Buckets de S4</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><ac:emoticon ac:name=\"cross\" ac:emoji-shortname=\":cross_mark:\" ac:emoji-id=\"atlassian-cross_mark\" ac:emoji-fallback=\":cross_mark:\" /></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Necesita cargar im&aacute;genes o datos est&aacute;ticos</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><ac:emoticon ac:name=\"cross\" ac:emoji-shortname=\":cross_mark:\" ac:emoji-id=\"atlassian-cross_mark\" ac:emoji-fallback=\":cross_mark:\" /></p></td></tr></tbody></table><h1>Cambios en la configuraci&oacute;n</h1><p>PR config Staging: &lt;LINK A PR&gt;</p><p>PR config Producci&oacute;n: &lt;LINK A PR&gt;</p><h1>Migraciones a ejecutar</h1><p>&lt;Listado de todas las migraciones que se deben ejecutar&gt;</p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"e48a3b3c-10e5-4a6d-bf71-f12393104bb2\"><ac:parameter ac:name=\"language\">sql</ac:parameter><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[CREATE TABLA ...]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro><h1>Datos a insertar</h1><p>&lt;Listado de datos que se necesitan insertar en tablas para que funcione la iniciativa&gt;</p><h2><span style=\"color: rgb(151,160,175);\">Commerce Service:</span></h2><p>CREACION DEL SERVICIO:</p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"829951f6-c4c4-4afe-be9c-de60c797732b\"><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[INSERT INTO services(name)VALUE('pix');]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro><p>CREACION DE LA ROLE_CATEGORY:</p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"71b907ec-88a1-435f-8c1f-86060415b2cc\"><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[INSERT INTO role_categories(name, description)VALUE('pix', 'PIX');]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro><p>CREACION DEL ROLE CAJERO PIX:</p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"5e301c21-e22b-4c97-8ce2-69b37308ef47\"><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[INSERT INTO roles(name, description, role_category_id)\nVALUES\n  ('pix_cashier', 'Cajero PIX', ->ID DEL ROLE_CATEGORY PIX<-),\n  ('pix_supervisor', 'Supervisor PIX', ->ID DEL ROLE_CATEGORY PIX<-);]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro><p>CREACION DE PERMISSIONS:</p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"78746cc3-5e00-4147-bb81-efa25c11f3da\"><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[INSERT INTO permissions(name, description)\nVALUES\n\t('services_pix', 'Servicio PIX'),\n\t('services_pix__cashier_basic_management', 'Servicio PIX -> Permisos de Cajero'),\n\t('services_pix__branch_management', 'Servicio PIX -> Permisos de Gestion De Sucursal'),\n\t('services_pix__all_branches_management', 'Servicio PIX -> Permisos de Gestión de Comercio');]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro><p>CREACION DE ROLE_PERMISSIONS:</p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"f8e6d1ef-3b2e-4fc2-8548-dd3a073f5961\"><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[INSERT INTO permission_roles\n\t(permission_id, role_id)\nVALUES\n\t(-> services_pix permission_id <-, -> superadmin role_id <-),\n\t(-> services_pix permission_id <-, -> pix_cashier role_id <-),\n\t(-> services_pix permission_id <-, -> pix_supervisor role_id <-),\n\t(-> __cashier_basic_management permission_id <-,-> pix_cashier role_id <-),\n\t(-> __all_branches_management permission_id <-,-> super_admin role_id <-),\n\t(-> __branch_management permission_id <-, -> pix_supervisor role_id <-);]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro><p>As&iacute; quedaron los inserts:</p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"b20470ae-6833-41b0-9cac-56e6fafdee82\"><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[INSERT INTO services(name) VALUES('pix');\n\nINSERT INTO role_categories(name, description) VALUES('pix', 'PIX');\n\nINSERT INTO roles(name, description, role_category_id)\nVALUES\n  ('pix_cashier', 'Cajero PIX', 12),\n  ('pix_supervisor', 'Supervisor PIX', 12);\n\nINSERT INTO permissions(name, description)\nVALUES\n  ('services_pix', 'Servicio PIX'),\n  ('services_pix__cashier_basic_management', 'Servicio PIX -> Permisos de Cajero'),\n  ('services_pix__branch_management', 'Servicio PIX -> Permisos de Gestion De Sucursal'),\n  ('services_pix__all_branches_management', 'Servicio PIX -> Permisos de Gestión de Comercio');\n\n\nINSERT INTO permission_roles (permission_id, role_id)\nVALUES\n  (93, 1),\n  (93, 60),\n  (93, 61),\n  (94, 60),\n  (96, 1),\n  (95, 61);]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro><h1>Pull requests a develop/master</h1><ul><li><p /></li></ul><p /><h1>Checklist deoendencias</h1><p>Redis version 6+ para compatibilidad con sidekiq</p><p>MySQL 8</p><p /><h1>Checklist</h1><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>ver que funcionen los logs. Ubicaciones de los logs. Puma, bancard loggers, external services, etc.</p></li><li><p>conexi&oacute;n a internet para pegarle a rendix</p></li><li><p>conectividad con pix-portal endpoint notify</p></li><li><p>credenciales de aplicacion para pix-service y pix-portal para autenticar requests entre servicios</p></li><li><p>Revisar conectividad con S4 y crear el bucket de reportes con el nombre <code>pix_reports</code></p></li><li><p>probar salida a internet desde contenedor pix-service para pegarle a rendix.</p></li><li><p>probar conectividad con auth-service, comerce-service, sentry.</p></li><li><p>configurar proxy dmz /pix/notifications para que apunte al proxy de servicios al puerto de pix service</p></li></ol><p /><p />","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2979037185"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":951},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2979037185/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2979037185/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2979037185/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2979037185/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2979037185","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2979037185/Deploy+a+producci+n+PIX+Service","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2979037185","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2979037185","tinyui":"/x/AYCQsQ","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}